=== Magadmi et al.\ 2019 — CADM1-Mediated Mast Cell-Nerve Adhesion Amplifies Inflammation

    / *Full Citation:*: Magadmi R, Meszaros J, Damanhouri ZA, Seward EP. CADM1-dependent adhesion between mast cells and sensory neurons enhances mast cell inflammatory responses. _Front Cell Neurosci_. 2019;13:262.
