    / *Full Citation:*: Lenze EJ, Mattar C, Zorumski CF, et al.\ Fluvoxamine vs Placebo and Clinical Deterioration in Outpatients With Symptomatic COVID-19: A Randomized Clinical Trial. _JAMA_. 2020;324(22):2292--2300.
